<br>
Also remember to skill up your 2hb skill. This can be done very easily for cheap with a Bamboo Bo stick, which used to run about 100-200 plat. I haven't seen the prices on them since the Bazaar opened up, but they probably are either the same or less expensive. This is a good weapon to use in your low leves, since it's going to be doing more than your hands do right now, but remember that you're going to want to upgrade fairly soon, since you will do more damage with other weapons than with your Bamboo Bo fairly quickly. It's primary use will be to bring up your skill quickly. The other weapon you might look for is an Adamantite Bo, which is a great damage delay weapon, but become less useful when you hit 30th level, and it starts to proc an AoE attack.<br>
<br>
Good luck!<br>
 <p>Fingal PeaceBringer </br>
