<br>
When I first started Korph I had an ubertwink friend (was using a jade mace!!!) and he gave me a Cane of the Tranquil, which I weilded in my main hand and fist in my offhand until about level 30 (at which point I transferred money from all my characters and bought a Jade Mace for myself, meh!).<br>
<br>
I'd try to get a fighting baton and use it in your main hand, fist in offhand.  That way your skills will remain up (my H2H wasn't maxed, but was nearly so).<br>
<br>
By the way, I am now 51 and using an IFS (sold the Jade Mace and Cane of the Tranquil, meh!) and kicking ass!<br>
<br>
It was funny when I was in KC and won the roll on a Jade Mace a few weeks back... lent it to a friend. <p>-Korph
